    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 27, "width": 24, "height": 3,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Access Log Analysis\n\nCloudFront access logs are delivered to `s3://aws-coder-microsites-logs/cloudfront-logs/`. For detailed geographic, per-page, and unique visitor analysis, query with **Amazon Athena**:\n\n```sql\nSELECT \n  date, \n  cs_uri_stem AS page,\n  COUNT(*) AS requests,\n  COUNT(DISTINCT c_ip) AS unique_visitors,\n  cs_headers_host_value AS country_code\nFROM cloudfront_logs\nWHERE cs_uri_stem LIKE '/aws+coder%'\nGROUP BY date, cs_uri_stem, cs_headers_host_value\nORDER BY requests DESC\n```\n\nLogs include: client IP, country, request URI, status code, bytes, user-agent, referer — enabling full visitor/session/geographic analysis."
      }
    }
  ]
